item.description:
@aznph8playa wrote:

Nice program but since everything is hard programmed and timed out, if there’s even a little lag, the program doesn’t run all the way through. I experienced this on level 13. Try using while loops with wait statements or repeats with until(getcolor(x,y)=colorofmarblemen) so that you can wait for the marble men to be in certain places before clicking.

Q. When will you be updating
A. Every other day I promise an update. But I sometimes will make it everyday

Q. I have an older version how do I update it.
